  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/970762d80ceb303df0223dff41f5782a.avif?t=1549892999\" width=460 height=214 /></span><br><br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人物介绍：</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/f376b3e0e70c351c42ae13f15f7edbdd.webp?t=1549892999\" width=32 height=48 /></span> Qi: A new entrant to the circus(genius magician).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/9b64289f75404f0a3019bf424f39ccf1.webp?t=1549892999\" width=32 height=49 /></span> Ning: Main member of the circus, who seems to know everything.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/85ac1842249c7cf0da7a2a88ce98b894.webp?t=1549892999\" width=32 height=48 /></span> Liu: Member of the circus, who agrees with Liao often (acting partner of Liao).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/f41d087645f859e6f5e3396107869bc3.webp?t=1549892999\" width=32 height=48 /></span> Liao: The circus chief, who inherits it from his father(responsible for the circus affairs).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/24adead9a6016bc5d7b512b0634d10b4.webp?t=1549892999\" width=32 height=48 /></span> Xiang: Main member of the circus, who is a wild animal trainer(the playmate of the pet Li).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/24f0a9822e0dd59ccf5a243f3ff70a03.webp?t=1549892999\" width=32 height=48 /></span> Ji: Main member of the circus, who is good at acrobatics of high difficulty.<br><br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction:</h2><br><br>The ceremony to worship demons is inaugurated in the World Center.<br><br>The mouth of sin is open, which will lead to the climax——<br><br>As a new member of the circus, tonight is his first show.<br><br>The whole family would welcome Qi’s coming, however, behind the peace and beauty of the night, <br><br>A violent orgy seems to wait for being triggered.<br><br>Qi is pushed near edge step by step because of the suddenly appeared “evil”, so-called “monster” <br><br>and the reality of people behind their masks.<br><br>How to escape? Our dear genius magician would bring you——<br><br>Ah, just a valueless story to kill the night.<br><br>Please be seated——<br><br>The show, is gonna begin.....<br><br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br>Different pictures,<br>with weird and suspenseful atmosphere,<br>and various plot branches.<br>This is a performance without a unified ending.<br>It concludes 6 different game endings.<br><br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/970762d80ceb303df0223dff41f5782a.avif?t=1549892999\" width=460 height=214 /></span><br><br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人物介绍：</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/f376b3e0e70c351c42ae13f15f7edbdd.webp?t=1549892999\" width=32 height=48 /></span> Qi: A new entrant to the circus(genius magician).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/9b64289f75404f0a3019bf424f39ccf1.webp?t=1549892999\" width=32 height=49 /></span> Ning: Main member of the circus, who seems to know everything.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/85ac1842249c7cf0da7a2a88ce98b894.webp?t=1549892999\" width=32 height=48 /></span> Liu: Member of the circus, who agrees with Liao often (acting partner of Liao).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/f41d087645f859e6f5e3396107869bc3.webp?t=1549892999\" width=32 height=48 /></span> Liao: The circus chief, who inherits it from his father(responsible for the circus affairs).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/24adead9a6016bc5d7b512b0634d10b4.webp?t=1549892999\" width=32 height=48 /></span> Xiang: Main member of the circus, who is a wild animal trainer(the playmate of the pet Li).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950160/extras/24f0a9822e0dd59ccf5a243f3ff70a03.webp?t=1549892999\" width=32 height=48 /></span> Ji: Main member of the circus, who is good at acrobatics of high difficulty.<br><br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction:</h2><br><br>The ceremony to worship demons is inaugurated in the World Center.<br><br>The mouth of sin is open, which will lead to the climax——<br><br>As a new member of the circus, tonight is his first show.<br><br>The whole family would welcome Qi’s coming, however, behind the peace and beauty of the night, <br><br>A violent orgy seems to wait for being triggered.<br><br>Qi is pushed near edge step by step because of the suddenly appeared “evil”, so-called “monster” <br><br>and the reality of people behind their masks.<br><br>How to escape? Our dear genius magician would bring you——<br><br>Ah, just a valueless story to kill the night.<br><br>Please be seated——<br><br>The show, is gonna begin.....<br><br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br>Different pictures,<br>with weird and suspenseful atmosphere,<br>and various plot branches.<br>This is a performance without a unified ending.<br>It concludes 6 different game endings.<br><br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------",
